      "formula": "J_(D,n,lambda)(z/D)=F_(n,lambda)(z)-z^2*F_(n,lambda)''(z)/(2*D)+O_K(D^(-2)); J_D(z/D)=F-z^2*F''/(2*D)+(z^3*F'''/3+z^4*F''''/8)/D^2+O_K(D^(-3))",
